    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks, while the transmission exhibits slipping; additionally, the body has extensive rust and the interior shows heavy wear. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor.",
