      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, featuring an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects a rigorous standard of care. Every component has been evaluated to ensure it meets our highest benchmarks for mechanical and aesthetic excellence. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
